effect:
If a Conductive space becomes _Electrified_ place another _Electrified_ space in an adjacent space. Spaces placed due to Conductive due not trigger this effect.
&nbsp;
When a creature in a Conductive space is attacked by an attack that deals _Lightning_ Damage add all contiguous Conductive spaces to the _Area_. Additionally, creatures in Conductive spaces have _Weakness_ 1 (_Lightning_), _Susceptible_ (_Shocked_).
